Do birds poop every time they take off?

Is BPD just PTSD?

BPD involves a generalized under-regulation of intense distress related to real or perceived abandonment or rejection, whereas emotion dysregulation in PTSD is characterized by attempts to over-regulate (e.g., emotional numbing, avoidance, dissociation) distress related to reminders of traumatic experiences. Is diagonals of rectangle are equal?

03 Sep 2024, 00:00

A rectangle is a parallelogram, so its opposite sides are equal. The diagonals of a rectangle are equal and bisect each other. Are the 2 diagonals of a rectangle is equal Why? Yes. The diagonals of a rectangle are of equal length. The two diagonals of a rectangle are the hypotenuse of the two right angled triangles. Since, the height and base of the two triangles are equal, by Pythagoras Theorem, the hypotenuse of the triangles are also equal.

Will I pee during surgery?

31 Aug 2024, 00:00

General anesthesia paralyzes the bladder muscles. This can make it not only hard to pee, but impact your ability to recognize you have to urinate altogether. Additionally, many surgeries involve the placement of a Foley catheter‚Äîa tube put in the body to drain urine from the bladder. Do people pee during surgeries? Urinary catheters are often used during surgery, as you can't control your bladder while under anesthesia. For this purpose, a foley catheter is typically placed prior to surgery and keeps the bladder empty throughout.

14 Creatures You Didn't Realize Were Pollinators

29 Aug 2024, 00:00

Mosquitoes are probably among the least popular of all of Earth's insects. Their bites can leave more than itchy red welts ‚Äî they can spread devastating illnesses like malaria, yellow fever, and Zika. Do you need a passport to leave Vatican City?

26 Aug 2024, 00:00

Yes, you need a passport to leave Vatican City. Despite its small size and unique status as a sovereign city-state, Vatican City operates like any other country when it comes to immigration and travel regulations. If you are planning to leave Vatican City and enter another country, you will be required to present your passport at the border controls. This is because Vatican City, although an independent state, does not have its own airport or seaport, which means that you will need to pass through the neighboring country of Italy to reach your final destination.

How do dragonflies drink?

Answer Dragonflies and their nymphs are fierce predators that prey on other insects. They hunt by sight, seeing prey as it moves and pursuing it. Nymphs need nourishment in order to grow big enough to undergo the transformation into adults.
